Debian/Ubuntu packaging
=======================

Place here:
- Dockerfile          — build environment image
- build-inside.sh     — script run inside the container to produce .deb packages

The Debian package rules (debian/ directory) are sourced from
damentz/liquorix-package at build time via the liquorix-package archive.
They do not need to be vendored here.

Reference: https://github.com/damentz/liquorix-package/tree/6.x/master/linux-liquorix/debian
